quran[18{c,v,t}:
68,43,"inn ki nigehain neechi hon gi, zillat inn par chhaa rahi hogi yeh jab sahih o salim thay uss waqt aِnhin sjday ke liye bulaya jata tha ( aur yeh inkaar karte thay )"
68,44,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum iss kalaam ke jhutlanay walon ka maamla mujh par chore do hum aisay tareeqa se inn ko batadreej tabahi ki taraf le jayen ge ke inn ko khabar bhi nah hogi"
68,45,"mein inn ki rassi daraaz kar raha hon, meri chaal barri zabardast hai"
68,46,kya tum inn se koi ajar talab kar rahay ho ke yeh is chti ke boojh taley dabey ja rahay hon ?
68,47,kya inn ke paas ghaib ka ilm hai jisay yeh likh rahay hon ?
68,48,"pas apne rab ka faisla sadir honay taq sabr karo aur machhli walay ( Younis aleh islam ) ki terhan nah ho jao, jab uss ne puraka tha aur woh gham se bhara howa tha"
68,49,agar is ke rab ki meharbani uss ke shaamil haal nah ho jati to woh mazmoom ho kar chtil maidan mein pheink diya jata
68,50,aakhir kaar uss ke rab ne usay bargzida farma liya aur isay Saleh bundon mein shaamil kar diya
68,51,"jab yeh kafir log kalaam nasiyaat ( quran ) suntay hain to tumhe aisi nazron se dekhte hain ke goya tumahray qadam ukhaar den ge, aur kehte hain yeh zaroor deewana hai"
68,52,halaank yeh to saaray Jahan walon ke liye aik nasiyaat hai
69,1,honishudni (waqay honay wali ghari)!
69,2,kya hai woh honi shudni ?
69,3,aur tum kya jano ke woh kya hai honishudni?
69,4,samood aur Aad ne uss achanak toot parney wali aafat ko jhtlaya
69,5,to samood aik sakht haadsa mein halaak kiye gay
69,6,aur Aad aik barri shadeed tofani aandhi se tabah kar diye gay
69,7,Allah taala ne uss ko musalsal saat raat aur aath din unn par musallat rakha ( tum wahan hotay to ) dekhte ke woh wahan iss terhan pchhrhe parre hain jaisay woh khajoor ke boseedah tanay hon
69,8,ab kya unn mein se koi tumhe baqi bacha nazar aata hai ?
